quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,Ma kuu yimid warka martidii Ibraahiim ee sharafta lahayd
  51,25,"Waa tii ay u soo galeen, oo yidhaahdeen: waa nabad, wuxuu yidhi: nabad. (waxaad tihiin) qolo aan la garaneyn"
  51,26,Markaasuu u laabtay dhinac xagga reerkiisii oo keenay dibi buuran oo shiilan
  51,27,"Oo u soo dhoweeyey (isagoo leh): Mawaydaan cunayn"
  51,28,"Markaas baa waxaa ka galay dareen cabsi ah. Waxay yidhaahdeen: Ha cabsan, oo waxay ugu bishaareeyeen wiil aqoon leh"
  51,29,"Markaas bay soo aadday haweeneydiisii iyadoo yaabban, oo iska dharbaaxday wejigeeda, oo tidhi: Ma habar ma dhasho ah oo duqowday"
  51,30,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Sidaas buu leeyahay Rabbigaa. Hubaal, waa Isaga Xakiimka ,Wax kasta Ogaha ah"
  51,31,"Wuxuu yidhi: Muxuu haddaba xaalkiinnu yahay kuwayahow la soo diray"
  51,32,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Hubaal waxaa naloo soo diray qolo dambiilayaal ah"
  51,33,Si aan ugu soo dirno korkooda dhagaxyo dhoobo ah
  51,34,Looga soo calaameeyey xagga Rabbigaa xadgudbayaasha
  51,35,Markaas baan ka soo bixinnay halkaa wixii ku jiray ee mu’miniin ah
  51,36,Kamase aanu helin gudaheeda wax aan aheyn hal guri oo muslimiin ah
  51,37,Oo waxaan uga tagnay halkaa Calaamo5 kuwa ka cabsada cadaabta xanuunka badan
  51,38,"Oo Muuse (calaamad baa ku sugan), markaan u dirnay Fircoon isagoo wata Xujo Cad"
  51,39,"Wuuse jeestay isagoo ay la jiraan ciidammadiisii oo yidhi: Waa saaxir ama nin waalan"
  51,40,Markaas baan qabannay isaga iyo askartiisiiba oo xoog ugu tuurnay badda isagoo eedeysan
  51,41,"Oo Caad (waxaa ku sugan calaamo), markaan ku dirnay dabayl wax halaagta"
  51,42,Wax kama tegin ay ku timid inay ka dhigtay maahee digada oo kale
  51,43,"Oo Thamuud (calaamaa ku sugan), markii lagu yidhi: Raaxeysta in muddo yar ah"
  51,44,"Waxayse ka madax adeygeen Amarka Rabbigood, markaasaa waxaa qabtay danab xoog leh iyagoo arkayey"
  51,45,"Sidaa darteed waa awoodi waayeen inay soo kacaan, isumana gargaari karin"
  51,46,"Oo qolodii Nuux iyaga hortood (waxaa ku sugan calaamo), hubaal waxay ahaayeen qolo caasiyaal ah"